script:
1). Weren't you going to fix the printer?
He wasn't going to.
No, you weren't.
Yes, I was. Sorry, I forgot. 
2). Would you like to take a break?
Not right now, thanks. 
I'm sorry I broke it.
Yes, I couldn't.
3). Has Jasmine arrived yet?
Yes, she will be here soon.
No, we expect her shortly. 
She doesn't drive.
